Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.00,Memory,,0,0,0,,Fujiwarano Sai, a go player from the Heian period...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:08.50,Memory,,0,0,0,,has passed through time and returned to\Nthe world in the mind of Shindou Hikaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:11.70,Memory,,0,0,0,,in order to obtain the Hand of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya, you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I heard him say "To surpass\NTouya Akira" in the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.76,0:02:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! I'm his, and he's my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too much of a gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:11.57,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: Yuugen translates roughly into\NSpiritual Wonder or Spiritual Mystery]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:11.57,Title_eps_top,,0,0,0,,{\fad(316,0)\fscx197\t(0,330,1,\fscx100)\blur0.8\pos(320,115)}The Twenty-Third Match
