Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.16,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs23.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(385,11)}S\Nh\Ni\Nn\Nd\No\Nu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.08,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it's all black!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya Akira's rival experiences\Nsix straight losses in a second class.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it!? What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I see! He's your rival at Shougi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.23,0:02:43.10,Sai,,0,0,0,,Don't mind him Hikaru, you're getting stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's your rank!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.14,Background,,0,0,0,,Waya... Waya...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs23.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(10,281)}O\Nd\Na
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs23.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(123,243)}M\Ni\Nu\Nr\Na
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs23.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(219,199)}W\Na\Ny\Na
