Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs23.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(536,129)}K\Na\Nn\Ne\Nd\Na
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.28,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs23.5\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(632,103)}Y\Na\Nm\Na\Nm\No\Nt\No
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.54,0:02:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,6th... in first class...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Waya you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the bottom of second class I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.39,0:03:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And still lost to Touya twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I lost to him, I'm a lot\Ncloser to Touya than you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Though he probably doesn't even know I exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.26,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.88,0:03:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pissed at myself for letting\NTouya beat me at the Pro exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't lose to him in spirit and skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I played against Touya-kun too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.02,Background,,0,0,0,,Touya doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all a matter of making yourself the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ochi, he's in the sixth grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.92,Background,,0,0,0,,He came three months before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.51,Background,,0,0,0,,Of course he started at the\Nvery bottom of second class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:55.29,Background,,0,0,0,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's third in first class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Third... in first class?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.40,Background,,0,0,0,,He probably thinks he'll pass the pro exams today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to pass them too this year, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pass this year, I won't\Nhave to go to High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like studying Waya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! The pain of having to listen to a\Nteacher for hours and hours everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be in the ninth grade by\Nthe pro exam in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pass it, I'll start as a pro\Nthe same time I graduate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to finally pass this year too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Isumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn 18 this year, it's the\Nlast year I can remain an Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, even if you're not an Insei,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.22,Background,,0,0,0,,you can take the pro exam until you're 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know all that. It's a matter of feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, and the year before that, I failed the\Npro exams despite being ranked one in the Inseis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.80,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,, If I fail this year too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel too sorry for myself to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people can pass the pro exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:04:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:04:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Just three!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.34,0:05:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a long way ahead on the path\Nyou're walking, six straight losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Long way... ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.85,Background,,0,0,0,,I didn't think that would work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this flow here, that's\Nnot good enough for black.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do you want us going after the 2 moku here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.26,Background,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, extend yourself here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.17,Background,,0,0,0,,Can you really win the battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.28,Background,,0,0,0,,Probably?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.91,Background,,0,0,0,,Probably!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about it Akira-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Is your mind filled with becoming pro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to say "finally". Akira-kun\Nis finally a pro starting in April.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What I don't understand is why you were fooling\Naround in the Go club when you joined Jr. High.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right Ogata-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But he had more spirit back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.13,Background,,0,0,0,,Go isn't all about skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In between the small difference in\Nskill, your emotions, your spirit affects\Nthe outcome of the game greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.94,0:06:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,not even worth pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel different...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-kun's a scary enough existence for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because you're losing one out\Nof every three matches, Ashiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya-Meijin probably knows\Nsince he plays him every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, once the matches begin in\NApril, the results will show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But Ashiwara-kun, how long do you plan on drifting\Nin between the first and second preliminaries?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free this Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Something to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.77,Background,,0,0,0,,Shindou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup! My first victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.92,0:07:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just about to start my winning streak now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:25.35,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Touya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he have some business with the teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No... he came to see if I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NHe completely ignored you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not your rival at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:15.13,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He said he'll never appear before me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.27,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He's waiting for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.74,Thinking,,0,0,0,,For me to rise to his level!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.00,0:08:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That he became Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Was he what you wanted to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if he is Insei?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that have to do with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably did it in pursuit of Touya Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Touya-kun you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect! Do you mind if I interview you for a bit?\NAbout becoming pro, and about your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you come to the publishing\Ndepartment upstairs later?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Ogata-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought he would motivate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! That's funny. To chase\Nafter me with his skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:30.70,Background,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll move forward far beyond\Nhim, so that he'll never reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him come near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's motivated you plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:59.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,What an interesting existence he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.41,Thinking,,0,0,0,,{\1c&HC5FEC1&}So he'll get pummeled here for awhile as Insei....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.11,Thinking,,0,0,0,,hurry up and come to the world of the pros...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:10.32,Thinking,,0,0,0,,no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.89,Thinking,,0,0,0,,will he be able to come at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:26.40,Background,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Imanishi-kun! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What is with his attitude? Just over losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.21,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You were Imanishi's opponent just now right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he make a stupid mistake somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. A total miscalculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's irritated because the High\NSchool entrance exams are coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Arigatou.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.30,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his grades at school were dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, if I had time, I'd be studying Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and if it pays off and we become pro,\Nit's all fine, but he's still second class.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And he lost to someone like Shindou because\Nof a stupid mistake, no wonder he's irritated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.84,0:11:10.82,Background,,0,0,0,,Hey, Touya doesn't study for school either right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's in Kaiou Jr. High, he must be really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Doesn't that irritate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really irritate me but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's irritating! He passed the\Npro exams in one shot too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:28.45,Background,,0,0,0,,He'll be appearing in the new first dan series soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:30.24,Background,,0,0,0,,New first dan series?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't know anything do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.85,0:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The new first dan series are matches\Nbetween people who just passed the\Npro exams, and the top pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to encourage new pros.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Encouragement huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You start as a pro in April, but we\Nhave a match like this before then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Last Tuesday, there was a match between\NKuwabara-sensei and Mashiba-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiba-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was an Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... so he passed the pro exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When Isumi-san and Waya failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the match go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He resigned helplessly before Kuwabara-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.28,0:12:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Touya should have it soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He keeps on moving forward doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.16,0:12:20.26,Background,,0,0,0,,It's not just Touya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.94,0:12:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who passed the pro\Nexams keeps moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We Insei, don't move forward at\Nall unless we pass the pro exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Zama-sensei! Ouza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouza?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one of the titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You should know the titles at the very least.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Zama-sensei! Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The day for your match against the\Nnew first dan has been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll send a notice for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's my opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Touya Akira-san. The Meijin's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Touya... him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposedly really strong according to\Nthe players studying under Touya-Meijin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course they won't say anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The new first dan series...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How have they been going? A\Nsweep by us experienced pros?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No there are losses as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... so they're letting the\Nnew players feel some glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a festival of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.89,0:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I'll let him win by half a moku too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.31,0:13:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everyone will like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.45,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"Touya Akira makes a great start as\Npro," your headlines will read better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well the publishers may appreciate it but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Kuwabara-sensei played\Nit a few days ago didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.79,0:14:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. His opponent was Mashiba-kun,\Nand he used to be Insei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like this please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.67,0:14:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he got nervous because\Nhe was playing Kuwabara-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,or maybe he went out of it because of the\Nroom of Yuugen, but he defeated himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.90,0:14:22.93,Background,,0,0,0,,Kuwabara-sensei went "Huh?" when Mashiba-kun\Nresigned, as if he played the game half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:26.05,Background,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuwabara-sensei can be quite a bully at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm hoping for a great game between a\Nhopeful new pro, and one of the top pros right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.79,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(427,17)}E\Nv\Ne\Nn\Nt\Ns\N\Nf\No\Nr\N\Nt\No\Nd\Na\Ny
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.79,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(347,58)}P\Nu\Nb\Nl\Ni\Nc\N\NM\Na\Nt\Nc\Nh\N\NR\No\No\Nm
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.79,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(276,58)}M\Ni\Nd\N\NK\Ny\Nu\N\NC\Nl\Na\Ns\Ns
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.79,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs24\pos(212,242)}N\Ne\Nw\N\NF\Ni\Nr\Ns\Nt\N\ND\Na\Nn\N\NS\Ne\Nr\Ni\Ne\Ns
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.79,NoteTimes,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs24\pos(91,257)}U\Ns\Ne\N\Nf\No\Nr\N\Nm\Na\Nt\Nc\Nh\Ne\Ns
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? Today!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you read the sign outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:15:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a match between Touya and the Ouza\Ntoday in the room of Yuugen in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a camera in the room\Nof Yuugen during matches,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can watch it on a monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.98,Background,,0,0,0,,It'll be shown on that TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We have our own matches,\Nso we can't watch all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can catch at least the second\Nhalf after your Insei matches are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I can't watch all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're here, wanna look\Nat the room of Yuugen as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What!? We're allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.87,Background,,0,0,0,,Here, this is the room of Yuugen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.98,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so dark, I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.21,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.20,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Sai...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.69,Sai,,0,0,0,,Maybe I feel it because of the state I'm in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.49,Sai,,0,0,0,,but the air here stings me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.95,Sai,,0,0,0,,Enough to make me smile\Nfrom quivering in anticipation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? Isn't it awesome?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the pros always play in places like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.07,0:16:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No. They usually play in the\Nmain room where we play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rooms like these are used only for title matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:36.47,Background,,0,0,0,,Using this room today, is kind of like\Nencouraging them to work hard so\Nthat they can play a real game in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year, I too will...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:49.68,Background,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking a memorial\Npicture before the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:17:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take some extras. He may\Nbecome big in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you face each other and converse a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.27,0:17:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Converse he said Touya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fighting you with all my\Nstrength today. My regards to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you have my regards as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared by my title of Ouza.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all the same once we're pro.\NYou can't win if you lose emotionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me thinking that\NI'm a new pro just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I intend to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:39.48,Thinking,,0,0,0,,He intends to do so? How arrogant of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:43.91,Background,,0,0,0,,Could you look this way please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:46.00,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Change of plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.05,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I'll crush him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.30,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Has Touya's match started yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:18:00.65,Sai,,0,0,0,,Hikaru, concentrate on the\Nmatch before you for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the first time you've been in\Nthe room of Yuugen right Touya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be your first time playing, but\Nyou've been in here before at least right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is a regular here.\NHave you never come with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never even sat here to\Nkeep time or record the moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not an Insei, so I've\Nnever kept time or records.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You were never an Insei?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But jobs like that come to new pros too right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd better learn how to do it by April.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:46.43,Thinking,,0,0,0,,Heh! How annoying, feel at least a little nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time, so we'll begin the match.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:54.11,Background,,0,0,0,,The new pro will move first, and\Nkomi is a reverse-komi, 5.5 moku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.70,Background,,0,0,0,,You each have 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.66,Background,,0,0,0,,After you use it, you have a\Nminute per move on the byouyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.40,Background,,0,0,0,,Well then. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.57,0:19:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ashiwara-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.99,Background,,0,0,0,,Oh yes! Ashiwara-sensei\Nstudies under Touya-Meijin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.43,0:19:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Touya-kun's friend. The closest to him in\Nage too. All of Touya-kun's friends are adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really calm. Every new pro I've seen\Nso far have been nervous or not confident,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Mashiba-kun, you were frozen stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.05,0:20:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuwabara-sensei was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:09.90,Background,,0,0,0,,Kuwabara-sensei slammed the stone onto\Nthe board really load on his first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe, you can't be getting swallowed\Nup by such obvious scare tactics.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuwabara-sensei's just the type of person to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see what happens with today's match.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.82,0:22:12.32,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1\pos(320,333)}Umezawa Yukari's Go Go Igo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.38,0:22:15.76,Note,,0,0,20,,{\an2\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Teacher Yukari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:16.83,Note,,0,0,20,,{\an2\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Yuuki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:19.66,Note,,0,0,20,,{\an2\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Mai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:25.14,Note,,0,0,100,,{\an2\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Mai might be in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:33.54,Note,,0,0,100,,{\an2\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Oh! They were captured!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Yuuki-kun, you took a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called Shichou when your stones\Nget captured in this stair like shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.33,0:22:41.82,Note,,0,0,115,,{\an2\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}Shichou.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.37,0:22:51.48,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}A method where you chase your opponent down\Nwith Atari after Atari, and then finally capture them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You go to Atari from where they escape,\Nand go to Atari from where they escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.04,0:22:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue this, black can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:22:55.02,Note,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\bord1\1c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\shad1}If you think a Shichou is going to\Nhappen, it's important to give up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.26,0:22:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get caught in Shichou, give\Nup as quickly as possible and look\Nfor another good place to move.
